The paper discusses the security and safety of DL systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the use of formal methods and software engineering in DL systems development, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of DL techniques for classification and recognition, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the verification of correctness in DL systems, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
